# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# NOCTIS RESERVE - PORTFOLIO SHOWCASE REPOSITORY CONFIGURATION
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# This .gitignore is specifically designed for a public portfolio showcase.
# It uses an aggressive "ignore everything, allow specific" policy to ensure
# NO sensitive backend code, credentials, or proprietary business logic 
# accidentally leaks into the public GitHub repository.
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# 1. Ignore EVERYTHING in the repository by default
/*

# 2. Allow PUBLIC-SAFE presentation directories and files
!/Frontend/
!/portfolio-assets/
!.gitignore
!README.md

# 3. Allow SPECIFIC SAFE backend elements (Domain layer)
# This allows recruiters/viewers to see C# Clean Architecture styling 
# without exposing the infrastructure, EF Core migrations, or business logic.
!/backend/
/backend/*
!/backend/src/
/backend/src/*
!/backend/src/ObsidianArchitect.Domain/
# Ensure only C# files are exposed in Domain (blocking bin/obj)
/backend/src/ObsidianArchitect.Domain/bin/
/backend/src/ObsidianArchitect.Domain/obj/
!/backend/src/ObsidianArchitect.Domain/**/*.cs
!/backend/src/ObsidianArchitect.Domain/*.csproj

# 4. EXPLICITLY DENY ANY SENSITIVE FILES OR FOLDERS
*.json
*.sql
*.binlog
*.txt
*.old
.env
.idea/
.vs/
*.user
*.suo
node_modules/
